track.name: Bemsha Swing
comments: An old dog, this brings me memories of my youth...Love all this jazz...
I am listening to a live version off an album called Azzuri and it's wonderful. I love how different Monk can make the same tune sound on different sessions, but then that's jazz.

"Never heard the wrong notes played so right."
Brilliant assessment there ...
Never heard the wrong notes played so right.
The bass, the drum, the piano, everything is so... amazing. Dont even know how to describe it
Still new and so groovy forty years after I first heard it on my first Monk LP bought off my first wages after leaving school
tried to find the RHCP cover; no luck. Mustardog? Alberina? Por favor.
You just can't keep your foot still....
